headline: Mizuho Lifts Seagate (STX) to $475, Citing Continued Storage Upswing
summary: We recently published an article titled 12 Best Data Storage Stocks to Buy Right Now. On February 17, Mizuho increased its price target on Seagate Technology Holdings plc (NASDAQ:STX) to $475 from $440 and maintained an Outperform rating, reflecting continued confidence in earnings momentum and favorable industry conditions within mass-capacity storage.
